<div class="default-container">
  <div class="theme-video">
   <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
     <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/q-eiR64vxfs"></iframe>
   </div>
 </div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
    <div class="thumbnail">
      <img src="<%= asset_path "themes/2.jpg", size: "175x175"%>" alt="...">
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>History</h3>
        <p>Discover the history of the Banjara. Where do they come from? How is it to live like a nomad?</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
    <div class="thumbnail">
      <img src="<%= asset_path "themes/interesting.png", size: "350x350"%>" alt="...">
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Fun Facts</h3>
        <p>Fun facts of Banjara culture. Did you know about the mysterious Bhaul? The magic, the dance and more.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
    <div class="thumbnail">
      <img src="<%= asset_path "themes/3.jpg", size: "175x175"%>" alt="...">
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Clothing</h3>
        <p>Banjara clothing is heavy, complex and colourful. It is their way to connect with the gods and keep bad omens away.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
    <div class="thumbnail">
      <img src="<%= asset_path "themes/5.jpg", size: "175x175"%>" alt="...">
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Tattoos</h3>
        <p>Did you know the Banjara have a long tradition of tattoos? It's a fascinating read.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
    <div class="thumbnail">
      <img src="<%= asset_path "themes/6.jpg", size: "175x175"%>" alt="...">
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Jewelry</h3>
        <p>As you might seen by the pictures, the Banjara people love turning simple objects like coins into elaborate jewelry.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
    <div class="thumbnail">
      <img src="<%= asset_path "themes/7.jpg", size: "175x175"%>" alt="...">
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Embroidery</h3>
        <p>For the Banjaras, clothing can't be perfect as only the gods are perfect. Discover more here.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="row">
  <%= render "home/countdown_timer" %>
</div>


</div>
